                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-184-18621215 t18621215-184-punishment-72"></join>Confined Eighteen Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The officer Holton stated that the prisoner had been several times convicted of assaults on the police.</hi>
